            "answer": "<p>At The Promise Ring Co. we are committed to providing you with<br/>exceptional service and ensuring that your purchase of your ring is a truly special and sentimental experience. We understand that these pieces aren't just jewellery; they are symbols of love, commitment, and cherished moments.</p><p>That's why we stand by our products and offer a 2-year guarantee to give you peace of mind.</p><p>For full warranty terms <a href=\"https://thepromiseringco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://thepromiseringco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\">click here</a></p>"
